                <li>ğŸ” SAST (Static Application Security Testing)</li>\
                <li>ğŸŒ DAST (Dynamic Application Security Testing)</li>\
                <li>ğŸ›¡ï¸ RASP (Runtime Application Self-Protection)</li>\
